title: Miss Bliss Wholefoods Kitchen
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out, Bakery, Catering, European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A relaxed breakfast and brunch cafe serving whole food without refined sugar. Supports local and organic produce. Has a nutrition index for navigation of menu. Vegan choices include granola bowl, toast toppings, falafel wrap, a few salads. Courtyard in the back.
